    <h1>A History of Public Permanent Common School Funds in the United States, 1795–1905</h1>
    <p class="byline">Fletcher Harper Swift, Ph.D. (Columbia) · Professor of Education, University of Minnesota · New York: Henry Holt and Company, 1911</p>

